Canada 's leading composite indicator advanced 0.4 pct December gaining 0.4 pct two previous month , Statistics Canada said .
The unfiltered index rose 0.8 pct month , turnaround 0.3 pct decline November , federal agency said .
The manufacturing group continued post advance good production rose 1.6 pct , third increase last four month .
The advance , however , offset deceleration household demand .
